 * - Compile: 
 *   - flex myCounter.l
 *   - gcc lex.yy.c -lfl -o myCounter
 * 
 * - Run: 
 *   - ./myCounter
 *   - ./myCounter < InputFile.txt
 * 
 * - Input:
 *   - Real-time user through stdin
 *   - Passing a file through stdin
 * 
 * - Output:
 *   - Number of Characters
 *   - Number of Words
 *   - Number of Lines
 *  
 * - Limits/Known bugs: 
 *   - Not iterable 
